ttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrwpaYu.jpg&h=b38cd696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好唔記得831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZuNAtv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZuNAtv.png&h=a8f19de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不反都出埋唔好再搵藉口唔出<br />\n1月1號維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n【元旦大遊行　不反已出】<br />\n<br />\n民陣已收到警方發出的不反對通知書，<br />\n可以正式同各位講多次，1.1 維園見！<br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行當日將會有超過 40 個新成立工會同大家見面，歡迎大家瞭解詳情，加入你所屬行業的工會，壯大抗爭的組織力量。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n一月一，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要齊心祝福<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ug7anh2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fug7anh2.png&h=2bf968e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fefa42842b73be0b1e4981c19e5f89b1aab3bed8","tid":1805874,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"462a237448e8624627dbd93e1e2f667d08dadb1a","tid":1805874,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:11:05.000Z","msg":"2019快將完結，香港行政長官林鄭月娥在最後一天送上一段影片，找來一系列的高官，叫大家和諧理性，希望香港盡快回復安寧。片段一開始時就拍低一系列「暴徒」破壞的設施，林鄭月娥聲稱會虛心聆聽，但又強調要一國兩制，一定要維護法治咁話。其他高官當然要強調，香港人要盡快恢復社會秩序，又講到自己有幾多幾多政績幫香港人咁話。以下是相關影片：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WhYmwJ3MA00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A